    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "I followed your suggestion @bobylito -> we only have items now. I also added a boolean `isFromSearch` to know if a searchForFacetsValues has been performed or not. \r\n\r\nThe next step about this PR are:\r\n* should we keep the facetQuery in our `searchState` (also see my previous comment on that)?\r\n* Should we merge both `searchResults` and `searchForFacetValuesResults`?\r\n* Once #1765 is merged, refactor code responsible to call the helper for SFFV\r\n* Fix the naming once the API is stable\r\n* Add the jsdoc & guide\r\n* Add this feature into one of our example?",
